               stealing a pair of silver shoe buckles, value 12 s. a pair of silver knee buckles, value 2 s. two pair of cotton stockings, value 1 s. a pair of thread stockings, value 1 s. a linen shirt, value 2 s. a guinea and half a guinea in monies, numbered, the property of 
